OL,3,CRestaurant customer jailed after
OL,4,Cstabbing chef in row over change
OL,6,FA Southampton restaurant customer who
OL,7,Fstabbed a worker in a row over change
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for five years.
OL,10,FJaypal Khaira, 33, of the Polygon, had
OL,11,Fdenied the charge of causing grievous
OL,12,Fbodily harm with intent but was found
OL,13,Fguilty by a jury in March.
OL,15,FHe was sentenced to five years
OL,16,Fimprisonment at Southampton Crown
OL,17,FCourt on Friday, 26 April. He will
OL,18,Fserve an additional three years on
OL,19,Flicence.
