OL,6,FThe court heard that on the evening of
OL,7,F13 April 2022 police were called to a
OL,8,Freport that a man in his 60s had been
OL,9,Fstabbed in the leg at the Jerk Pan
OL,10,FCaribbean restaurant on Commercial
OL,11,FRoad.
OL,13,FThe jury heard how Khaira had entered
OL,14,Fthe restaurant via the back entrance
OL,15,Ffollowing an earlier dispute with
OL,16,Fstaff about change.
