OL,6,FHe attempted to gain access to the
OL,7,Ffront of the premises and when a
OL,8,Fmember of staff tried to stop him he
OL,9,Fstabbed him in the thigh with a knife
OL,10,Fthat had been on a nearby counter.
OL,12,FPolice officers attended and arrested
OL,13,FKhaira at the scene, while the victim
OL,14,Fwas taken to hospital for treatment.
