OL,6,FDetective Constable Callum Whitehouse,
OL,7,Ffrom Hampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,8,FConstabulary, said: "Khaira's actions
OL,9,Fthat evening were reckless and
OL,10,Fextremely concerning. Thankfully, the
OL,11,Fvictim did not sustain serious
OL,12,Finjuries however just a few
OL,13,Fmillimetres difference and he would
OL,14,Flikely have been in a life threatening
OL,15,Fcondition.
